entries.femaleVariant: Wait... Footsteps.
Has to be a 'runners' nest 'round here somewhere.
Patrol.
Ever think back? About why we did it?
Why we took on the corps, strapped in leather, chrome and iron?
Dunno, Johnny. We were young – hot blood in our veins, shit judgment in our heads, like all pups.
We find it, slot in the backdoor shard, let Cunningham run wild.
What's the sitrep?
Cooling systems are down.
A diversion – handle it. The rest of you, get ready.
Understood!
Oh, fuck stealth!
My treat, eh? Old people with stories of de olden days – just like me grandparents.
Bullshit.
Two thousand sixty-seven – an Arasaka bodyguard shields the Emperor of Japan from an assassin's bullet.
Two thousand seventy-one – Arasaka security forces prevent mass riots in San Francisco, saving the city from certain ruin.
Two thousand seventy-four  – an Arasaka investigation eliminates a terror cell in Rio de Janeiro, ending a string of attacks and executing those responsible.
Two thousand seventy-six – Arasaka's counterintelligence division effectively secures a corporate summit in Jakarta, foiling forty-five plots to attack and sabotage it.
How will Arasaka shine in two thousand seventy-seven? That depends on you.
Made a run for it, wound up turret fodder.
Oh shit…
C'mon, the way down's beyond the door.
Let's move it!
Looks like our work here is already done.
I'm preparing to repel a netrunner attack originating from outside the facility.
Shiteaters never even stood a chance…
Seems Cunningham's made strides these last decades.
Arasaka netrunners have stormed the tower's systems.
Stopping their advance is my priority. Continue on your way alone.
I've cleared a path, but you must hurry. An elite security unit is following you.
We fought for beauty. Not knowin' what was good or true, was only the beautiful that meant a damn thing to us.
Did what…?
Don't let your mind wander. We'll kick around old brain cells over vodka once we're done.
Know that look. Got somethin' on your mind?
You will be on your own now.
And you must hurry. An Arasaka elite force isn't far behind.
Holy fuckin' Christmas… Who is she?
See, Johnny? You disappear from her life, she spreads her wings. Her and everyone else.
A woman pushed to the very edge.
